					<span>æŒ‘æˆ¦</span>ã€<span>æˆé•·</span>ã€ãã—ã¦<span>è±Šã‹ãªæš®ã‚‰ã—</span>ã¸ã®æ¢æ±‚ã€‚
				</p>
			</section>

			<hr class="divider animate-divider" />

			<section class="focus-areas">
				<h2 class="section-title reveal-item">Explore by Topic / ãƒˆãƒ”ãƒƒã‚¯ã‹ã‚‰æ¢ã™</h2>

				<div class="grid">
					{CATEGORIES.map((cat, index) => (
						<a 
							href={`/blog/${cat.slug}`} 
							class="card reveal-item"
							/* ãƒˆãƒ”ãƒƒã‚¯ãŒä¸¦ã‚“ã§è¡¨ç¤ºã•ã‚Œã‚‹éš›ã®ã‚ãšã‹ãªæ™‚é–“å·®ã‚’ç¶­æŒ */
							style={`transition-delay: ${index * 0.1}s;`}
						>
							<h3>{cat.label}</h3>
